# Base URL of the Go API. Leave empty in local dev (Vite proxies /api to :8080).
# In production (Vercel), set this to the Render service URL, e.g. https://eightfivetwo-api.onrender.com
# The Vercel Edge Middleware (apps/web/middleware.ts) also reads this to fetch collection/design data for OG meta tags.
VITE_API_URL=
